channel.title: Help with this ish!
channel.description:
Trying to put server on to my VPS.
Idk how. I was told to download FileZilla.
I'm using the correct credentials for filezilla but it still won't connect. If anyone can help me i'll rep++
I have Team Viewer too.

item.title: Help with this ish!
item.dc:creator: @frostyboy07 frostyboy07
item.description:
@frostyboy07 wrote:

Upload the files to www.uppit.com or www.mediafire.com and then download them onto your VPS, by using the Internet on your VPS and then run the server.

If you use no-ip, then make sure it’s downloaded, installed and ran correctly on your VPS.

That’s how I ran my server, simple.
